Campfire
========

Install Notes
-------------

  1. subdomain is your campfire subdomain 
	(ie 'your-subdomain' if you visit 'http://your-subdomain.campfirenow.com')

  2. room is the actual room name, not the id


Developer Notes
---------------

data
  - subdomain
  - email
  - password
  - room
  - ssl
  - play_sound

payload
  - refer to docs/github_payload
